#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.associative_scan"
msgstr "# triton.language.associative_scan"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.associative_scan` 对输入tensor沿指定轴应用关联扫描操作，使用combine_fn函数组合元素并更新进位值。"
msgstr "Introduction: `triton.language.associative_scan` applies an associative scan operation to the input tensor along the specified axis, using the `combine_fn` function to combine elements and update the carry value."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.associative_scan(input, axis, combine_fn, reverse=False, _semantic=None, _generator=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` 或 `tuple of Tensor` | 输入tensor，可以是单个tensor或tensor元组 |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | 沿着哪个维度进行关联扫描操作 |\n"
"| `combine_fn` | `Callable` | 用于组合两个标量tensor组的函数（必须用@triton.jit标记） |\n"
"| `reverse` | `bool` | 是否沿轴的反方向应用关联扫描|\n"
"| `_semantic` | `Optional[str]` | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
"| `_generator` | `Optional[Generator]` | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Description |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` or `tuple of Tensor` | Input tensor, can be a single tensor or a tuple of tensors |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | The dimension along which to perform the associative scan operation |\n"
"| `combine_fn` | `Callable` | Function for combining two groups of scalar tensors (must be decorated with `@triton.jit`) |\n"
"| `reverse` | `bool` | Whether to apply the associative scan in the reverse direction along the axis |\n"
"| `_semantic` | `Optional[str]` | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"
"| `_generator` | `Optional[Generator]` | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：对输入tensor沿指定轴应用关联扫描操作，使用combine_fn函数组合元素并更新进位值之后的tensor。\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: The tensor after applying the associative scan operation along the specified axis to the input tensor, using the `combine_fn` function to combine elements and update the carry value.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/associative_scan.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

